<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="486" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,1265,1470]" box="[199,1179,1301,1326]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,1017,1301,1326]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">Recorded damage and economic importance in the orchards of Iran:</emphasis>
Not recorded.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,1265,1470]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,937,1337,1362]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">Recorded damage in the orchards of other parts of the world:</emphasis>
It tested positive for stolbur phytoplasma in vineyards (
<bibRefCitation box="[274,515,1373,1398]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486" refId="ref21144" refString="Orenstein, S., Zahavi, T., Nestle, D., Shardon, R., Barkalifa, M. &amp; Weintraub, P. G. (2003) Spatial dispersion patterns of potential leafhopper and planthopper (Homoptera) vectors of phytoplasma in wine vineyards. Annals of Applied Biology, 142 (3), 341 - 348. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1744 - 7348.2003. tb 00259. x" type="journal article">
Orenstein 
<emphasis box="[392,441,1373,1398]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">et al</emphasis>
. 2003
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation box="[525,762,1373,1398]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486" refId="ref21229" refString="Orsagova, H., Brezikova, M. &amp; Schlesingerova, G. (2011) Presence of phytoplasmas in hemipterans in Czech vineyards. Bulletin of Insectology, 64 (Supplement), 119 - 120." type="journal article">
Orsagova 
<emphasis box="[640,688,1373,1398]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">et al</emphasis>
. 2011
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,1265,1470]" box="[199,1275,1409,1434]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="1915496054" box="[199,1275,1409,1434]" country="Iran" location="Alborz" pageId="11" pageNumber="486" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Alborz">
