</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,1265,1470]" box="[199,1320,1445,1470]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,342,1445,1470]" pageId="11" pageNumber="486">Conclusion:</emphasis>
The status of this species as a potential phytoplasma vector needs to be studied in Iran.
</paragraph>
